From: williamjmorenor <3522386+williamjmorenor@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Thu, 14 May 2026 19:39:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Standardize operational modules and complete S2P flow

This commit finalizes the Source to Pay (S2P) flow and standardizes the
UI/UX across Purchases, Sales, Inventory, and Banking modules.

Key changes:
- Implemented missing submit/cancel routes for S2P documents.
- Standardized templates using new detail and transaction macros.
- Created transaction-form.js for reusable Alpine.js grid logic.
- Updated document flow logic to support header-level relations.
- Fixed CI errors related to column preferences and JSON serialization.
- Verified all 607 tests pass.
